insights.text: Vuori is uniquely balanced: 42% women's / 40% men's. Alo skews 52% women's, Gymshark 24% men's.
Vuori's earth tone palette (16%) is +9% vs industry avgreinforcing California lifestyle positioning.
Jogger battle: Vuori (141) vs Lululemon (93). Vuori leads by 48.
Neutrals (black/white/gray/navy) = 49% of Vuori's palette. Core basics that drive repeat purchases.
Vuori leads Lululemon in men's: 1172 vs 727 products. A 61% advantage.
Vuori ranks #2 in shorts with 443 products. Behind Gymshark (775).
Outerwear depth: Vuori has 434 products vs Lululemon's 244. Key for cooler weather expansion.
Market context: 15,027 competitor products tracked. Vuori's 2,909 = 16% share of tracked catalog.
